description: Jersey Dawgs is a South Florida food truck serving up all your Garden State favorites, from the ripper dog, a popular hot dog which is specially made to be deep fried until the casing 'rips,' to the homemade chili, meatballs on a stick, and more! If you're in the mood for some disco fries or a Jersey burger, head on over to Jersey Dawgs and get yourself a good meal today!
name: Jersey Dawg
